                        &lt;p class=&quot;Aucunstyledeparagraphe&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Garamond&amp;quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Utsaah;mso-bidi-font-family:
